"Thank you," he says, his voice thick with emotion as he pushes the coins toward you. "The rest is yours when you bring Lily back to me. She's all I have." He then fumbles with a pack at his side. "I don't have much else, but I grabbed this from the farm... It's dark in those caves. Please, take it." He hands you a sturdy, unused torch.

